      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIMPLY FRIENDS (4) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Bottom Up - Grade 6 winner three back (20.26) at this track over 350m. Better than latest and can atone here. PAW AMARAN (2) flew the lids with a strong early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by 2 lengths over 400m at Warragul (23.11). Likely to be in the finish. REDBACK EXPRESS (7) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only one length (20.20) behind Rita Staff at this track. Will give a great sight again. REDEEMER BELLE (3) placed last time out at big odds - worth considering.",
